description: Tyler Sin is just starting out in 'the biz', and isn't so keen on the ins and outs. Austin Wilde is always looking for a fresh face, and is more than willing to mentor someone in the old In & Out. Besides, what Tyler lacks in business savvy, he more than makes up for in other ways. It's not like it would be first time Austin had to show someone the rope... er, ropes!Enjoy!
title: Workin' For It
